---
title: My luxee - Keep in touch with luxury stores
---

  <div id="wrapper">
    
    <div class="container text-right">
      <h1>LUXURY STORES'
      <br>COMMUNITY OF SALES ASSOCIATES
      </h1>

      <h2>Your global shopping assistant</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="vertical-spacer"></div>

    <div class="container text-right">
      <h3>Close to the Customers</h3>
      <h3>Close to the Brands</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center blinking">
      <% link_to '#benefits' do %>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary pulse">Is that all ?
        <br><i class="fa fa-angle-down fa-2x"></i>
        </button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
 
  </div>

  <div class="container padded" id="benefits">

    <div class="container text-left title">
      <h3>KEEP IN TOUCH WITH LUXURY STORES !</h3>
    </div>

     <div class="vertical-spacer"></div>

    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="features" data-sr="wait 0.2s, over 0.7s, scale up 30%">
        <%= image_tag "locate.svg" %>
          <p>
            Locate sales associates who speak your own language
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="features" data-sr="wait 0.4s, over 0.7s, scale up 30%">
          <%= image_tag "availability.svg" %>
          <p>
            Contact available assistants, a regular, according to their timetables
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="features" data-sr="wait 0.6s, over 0.7s, scale up 30%">
          <%= image_tag "notify.svg" %>
          <p>
            Give notice of your visit, chat for personal advice and setting goods aside
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <div class="features" data-sr="wait 0.8s, over 0.7s, scale up 30%">
          <%= image_tag "rating.svg" %>
          <p>
            Rate your shopping experience
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="container text-center">
    <h3>Oh oh, you caught us before we're ready...</h3>
    <p>We're working hard to finish our app soon. If you'd like us to send you a reminder when we're ready, just put your email in below :</p>
     <form class="form-inline" role="form" action="//myluxee.us11.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=b7959a16cabf22b1008be1d01&amp;id=faf2916d4c" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form">
       <input type="email" name="EMAIL" class="form-control" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="email address" required>
       <input type="submit" value="Remind me" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">
     </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="padded" id="About">

    <div class="container text-left title">
      <h3>WHAT</h3>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="title"><strong>EXTRAS FOR ALL</strong></p>
        <%= image_tag "associates.svg" %>
      <p>  
        <strong>SALES ASSOCIATES</strong>
        <br>Tell and retain customers
      </p>
      <ul class="list-unstyled text-center">
        <li>Emphase your position</li> 
        <li>Multiply your contacts</li>
        <li>Rise your commissions</li>
        <li>Update your information in real time</li> 
      </ul>
    </div> 

    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-6">
          <%= image_tag "customer.svg" %>
          <p>
            <strong>CUSTOMERS / PERSONAL SHOPPERS</strong>
            <br>Adopt a great multilingual assistant
          </p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li>Notify your visit </li> 
            <li>Click for trying and setting aside </li> 
            <li>Improve your shopping session thanks to original information</li> 
            <li>Keep a privileged link to the teams of points of sale</li>
          </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <%= image_tag "store.svg" %>
            <p>
              <strong>BRANDS' STORES</strong>
              <br>Take it easy, it is only productivity
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>Rise the traffic</li>
              <li>Involve your teams, reduce the turn-over</li>
              <li>Strengthen your stores' image and attractiveness</li>
              <li>Collect data and unbiased return of the customer experience</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>   

    <div class="container text-left title">
      <h3>WHY</h3>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-center title"><strong>PEOPLE BUY FROM PEOPLE - EVEN MORE SO IN LUXURY</strong></p>

    <div class="container text-justify">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
          <p>
            MyLuxee is an easy web-to-store solution that maintains the relationships between the retail luxury stores and their clients.
            <br>The plateform creates close links, allowing customers to get in touch with theirs favorite stores thanks to privileged contacts with the salespeople.
            <br>MyLuxee is a new shopping experience, borned out of two basic admissions in the luxury retail industry.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
          <p>
            For luxury shoppers, there is nothing better than dealing with sales associates they know well. Regular clients even call them by their first names.
            <br>Abroad or in places they know less, they often prefer being understood and advised by those who speak their own language. 
            <br>Brands hire specialists, fluent, but these are not always at full disposition due to different timetables.
          </p> 
        </div>
      </div> 
    </div>

    <div class="container text-center">
      <p>
        <strong>WHY NOT</strong> being aware of sales' availability and contacting them straight ?
        <br>Who better than the salespeople can advise you personally, book a good or even reserve some time for you ?
        <br>Let stores' sales associates become your fixers, let them be your <strong>luxees</strong> !
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container text-left title">
      <h3>WHO</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-xs-6">
          <h4>Clément TANGUY</h4>
          <%= image_tag "ClementTANGUY.jpg", class: "img-circle" %>
          <p>
            Autodidact, dabbler, luxury retail soldier,
            <br>I think human should ever be first in its digital issues.
            <br>That's why I founded MyLuxee.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
          <h4>Want you !</h4>
          <%= image_tag "profile-photo.jpg", height: 100, class: "img-circle" %>
          <p>
            Coding, designing, marketing ?
            <br>Participate to this community project.
            <br>Join a unique disruptive adventure.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>    
    </div>  
  </div>

  <script>

    window.sr = new scrollReveal();

  </script>
